<p><img style="float: right;" alt="eden-training" src="http://www.edenhrconsulting.com/images/stories/eden-stick-figures/eden-training.jpg" height="273" width="300" />At Eden HR we ensure that your training needs analysis, links in with the wider remit of developing your employees.</p>
<p>We work very closely with you on firstly, understanding what you have in place already, and secondly, to undertake an analysis to identify any potential gaps. We would then work in partnership with you to discuss the various development options open to you, and then design and deliver a programme of workshops fit for purpose.</p>
<p>As with every piece of training or coaching intervention we take at Eden HR, we always follow this up with an evaluation and review with a means to ensuring the development intervention is sustainable, to your business moving forward.</p>
<p>We can work with you to develop training plans for individuals, teams, departments and also on a company wide basis linking these to longer term business objectives.</p></td>
